Interface FragmentPackageImpl.Literals

Enclosing class:
FragmentPackageImpl
public static interface FragmentPackageImpl.Literals
Defines literals for the meta objects that represent
  • each class,
  • each feature of each class,
  • each enum,
  • and each data type
